R BGCOLOR=#E5E5E6><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/urugenpayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rugen payne</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>w4nn4b3!</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>4/24/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>1:51:49 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.darke.net/~alex/rugenpixel.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Anti - Cleric (druid/wiz ) RANT</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Tonight, after a vox raid, I ran through everfrost and received a few rez requests. Not uncommon, I'm pretty used to it. Not many clerics hang out in that part of the world, and you do end up with some higher end folks hunting the giants. One was even as I was about to zone into BB asking for a rez in perma, so I gated back to SafeHall, ran to zone, rezzed, and started the run over. One zone isn't so bad you can't do it over. *shrugs*<br>
<br>
I really and truly don't mind stuff like that.<br>
<br>
But then, on that second pass through, I'd decided to hook up with some friends, and so was on my way to the NK area. As I ran down into BB, there were two naked looking barbarians running down the tunnel, being chased by 3 gnolls. I nuked two of them, buffed the barb that was standing there trying to fight, and ran off after giving him a heal that should have more than taken care of him considering the buffs I tossed on him.<br>
<br>
Apparently what I didn't notice was the other barb with him got dropped by the gnolls. I was zoning into WK as I got the tell from his friend "Can I have a rez?"<br>
<br>
Once in WK, I made the quick spot assesement of my situation. Meeting with friends, rez request. I do a /who all soandso, and see that he's 5th level. Now I like to help out as much as the next guy, But I'm not going to turn back around and run BACK through 2 zones just to rez a 5th level person. I'm sorry. It's just not going to happen. If I had been right there and saw his body? I would have revived him or something. I honestly thought he had just high tailed it to the zone and zoned.<br>
<br>
So I send back that I'm already 2 zones away and that he'll need to run back to BB himself, that I'm sorry......<br>
<br>
<br>
[Mon Apr 23 22:41:35 2001] xxxxx tells you, 'can you rez me'<br>
